[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0998","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0998.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1174","title":"Iomega ZIP-100 安全绕过漏洞","description":"Iomega ZIP-100 磁盘驱动器存在安全绕过漏洞，攻击者在拥有物理接触磁盘驱动器的条件下，可先插入已知密码的磁盘，待驱动器断电后手动替换为目标磁盘，再利用已知密码访问受保护的目标磁盘内容。该漏洞源于密码验证机制仅验证磁盘而非驱动器的设计缺陷，影响所有使用 ZIP-100 驱动器的系统，需物理接触才能利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1174"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2001-12-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.640","remediation":"由于该漏洞源于 ZIP 驱动器硬件密码验证机制的局限性，建议：1）禁止将敏感数据存储在仅依赖 ZIP 驱动器硬件密码保护的磁盘上，改用软件加密方案（如 VeraCrypt、BitLocker）加密磁盘内容；2）物理管控 ZIP 磁盘的访问权限，确保磁盘在不使用时安全存放；3）废弃磁盘须进行物理销毁或消磁处理，防止被攻击者通过磁盘替换手法绕过密码访问数据。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.counterpane.com/crypto-gram-9812.html#doghouse","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad08212eac84f46206c2da8a50436d48e5ad608c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1174.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1174","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1174.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/baa4573f2fa6813cfbc3f5cda2f1796a92d64bdf/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1174.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x6rf-984m-fvfr/GHSA-x6rf-984m-fvfr.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88929/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1174.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_151800_151900.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/b2f46398fe44a78cde72b37ec1d56278cb4dcc92/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0998.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1144","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1144.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1514","title":"Celtech ExpressFS FTP 服务器远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ExpressFS FTP 服务器 2.x 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当攻击者向 FTP 服务的 USER 命令发送超长字符串时，可触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致 FTP 服务进程崩溃造成拒绝服务，在特定条件下可进一步实现远程代码执行。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用该漏洞，只需网络可达目标 FTP 端口（默认 21）即可发起攻击。该漏洞影响 Celtech ExpressFS FTP 服务器 2.x 全版本，危害等级高，建议用户尽快升级至修复版本或迁移至其他受支持的 FTP 服务软件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1514"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-11-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:36.223","remediation":"ExpressFS FTP Server 2.x 厂商已停止支持且无安全补丁发布，最彻底的修复措施是停止使用该产品，迁移至主动维护的 FTP 服务器如 vsftpd 或 FileZilla Server。临时缓解措施可在防火墙层面限制对 FTP 端口（21/TCP）的访问来源 IP，仅允许可信主机连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94121377716133&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94130292519646&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/749","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3401","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1514.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1514","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1514.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1514.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce70cbcf8165046f2229cbe0d9f53c47bf63ece0/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-87hw-jg6c-ggf2/GHSA-87hw-jg6c-ggf2.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/749/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_151700_151800.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1514.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7ab4292b-6860-4a16-8474-66e7c991e0ac.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8200d63179d89b9076027cd96356d55ef8a5349e/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1144.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0877","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0877.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1024","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9101,\"outputTokens\":24,\"totalTokens\":10853}}","description":"LBL tcpdump 3.4a 版本的 ip_print 处理函数存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送零长度头部的特制数据包，触发 tcpdump 在打印数据包时陷入无限循环并导致核心转储，从而实施拒绝服务攻击。该漏洞影响 LBL tcpdump 3.4a 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，属高危漏洞。攻击者无需认证即可远程发送恶意数据包触发漏洞，导致 tcpdump 进程崩溃并产生核心转储文件，造成服务拒绝。ExploitDB 已公开相关利用代码（tcpdump 3.4 - Protocol Four / Zero Header Length）。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1024"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-11-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.747","remediation":"建议将 LBL tcpdump 升级至 3.4a7 及以上修复版本（或迁移至 tcpdump 3.5 以上版本），该版本修复了 ip_print 对零长度头部数据包的无限循环缺陷。如无法立即升级，可在抓包主机的前端防火墙或路由器上过滤畸形 IP 包，并避免在非信任网络接口上以 root 权限运行 tcpdump 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92955903802773&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92963447601748&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92989907627051&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/313","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19251","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7e65fa522cff0172990568230ff9b719b8650296/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1024.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1024","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1024.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/7aedbd0209e609a1924ad29a8dda684737576137/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1024.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4xf9-whrj-cqwc/GHSA-4xf9-whrj-cqwc.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1024.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_151700_151800.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a2475725-573a-44a3-9fee-e5b8ed92fad2.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0877.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0877.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0877.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1191","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1191.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1569","title":"ID Software Quake 1.9 UDP 洪水拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Id Software 出品的 Quake 1 及 NetQuake 游戏服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者可通过伪造源地址，向目标服务器持续发送大量 UDP 连接请求数据包，触发服务器对连接资源的不当处理，导致资源耗尽或正常玩家被强制断开连接。该漏洞影响运行 Quake 1（1.9 版本）及 NetQuake 服务的服务器，攻击者可利用任何能发送 UDP 数据包的网络主机远程发起，无需身份认证，只需具备向目标服务器网络可达的条件即可造成服务不可用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1569"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2001-07-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:44.320","remediation":"建议将 Quake 1.服务器升级至官方后续修复版本（id Software 发布的 1.09 及以上补丁版本），启用服务端内置的连接速率限制与玩家上限保护；在网络层面通过防火墙或路由器对来自单个源 IP 的 UDP 6112 端口（Quake 默认端口）连接请求进行限速与伪造源过滤，并对未知来源 UDP 流量做丢包策略，以缓解 UDP 洪泛造成的资源耗尽与强制断连。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221101925989&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91012172524181&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/197268","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/3051","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/6871","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/21012","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2218edc43f34225d168835de417dff40749bef5/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1569.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1569","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1569.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2119b082f4927b0a9c902ed9fe95efb3b301cb81/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1569.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j5v7-8m23-gqjv/GHSA-j5v7-8m23-gqjv.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x4000/3051/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1569.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--33d35062-c5b9-4856-af57-c385fc9cb732.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/44b40554314aa90807d3ddee27488f8c21cbcd40/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--33d35062-c5b9-4856-af57-c385fc9cb732.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1191.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1191.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1191.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0739","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0739.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0945","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server Internet Mail Service 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.0 和 5.5 的 Internet Mail Service (IMS) 组件中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器的 25 端口发送特制的 AUTH 或 AUTHINFO 命令，触发 IMS 在处理这些命令时的缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Exchange Server 5.0 和 5.5 版本，攻击者只需能够与目标建立 SMTP 连接即可实施攻击，利用门槛较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0945"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:22.897","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft Exchange 5.5 Post-Service Pack 2 安全汇总更新，或升级至受支持的 Exchange Server 2016/2019 版本。如无法立即升级，可在网络防火墙或 Exchange 前端限制对 SMTP 端口 (25/TCP) 的 AUTH/AUTHINFO 命令访问，仅允许可信来源发起认证请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ169174","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-080.shtml","http://xforce.iss.net/alerts/advise4.php","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1223","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58316128f65d22a226717ff1f92ebf2058e46bc6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0945.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0945","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0945.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4d2ed764072119c12b6f84e