.osvdb.org/3236","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1742","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0924.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0924","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0924.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/263f37bc67cd24fe03a39077d8b57f3001369a95/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0924.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qv3g-7qpf-gwrv/GHSA-qv3g-7qpf-gwrv.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0924.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d2f00bb5-c7b8-4a10-bcbe-d7155e27240e.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--d2f00bb5-c7b8-4a10-bcbe-d7155e27240e.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0724.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0723","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0723.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0923","title":"Allaire ColdFusion Server 示例代码片段文件读取与拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ColdFusion Server 4.0 中的示例可运行代码片段存在安全漏洞，远程攻击者可利用这些代码片段读取服务器上的任意文件、发起拒绝服务攻击，或将服务器作为 HTTP 代理用于其他恶意请求。该漏洞源于 ColdFusion 默认安装时附带的示例文件未进行充分的访问控制，攻击者无需身份认证即可通过构造特制 HTTP 请求触发。受影响版本为 ColdFusion Server 4.0，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议删除或限制对示例目录的访问以缓解风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0923"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.250","remediation":"升级到 ColdFusion 5.0 或更高版本，该漏洞在后续版本中已修复。如无法升级，删除 ColdFusion Server 4.0 安装目录下的 `/cfdocs/examples/` 和 `/cfdocs/snippets/` 等示例目录，或通过 Web 服务器配置限制对这些目录的访问。由于 Allaire 公司已被 Macromedia（后为 Adobe）收购，建议迁移至 Adobe ColdFusion (2023/2021) 以获得持续安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.allaire.com/handlers/index.cfm?ID=8739&Method=Full","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0923.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0923","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0923.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/263f37bc67cd24fe03a39077d8b57f3001369a95/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0923.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q564-q586-w56h/GHSA-q564-q586-w56h.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0923.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_150600_150700.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f4b1193f-0cfe-429b-be60-e3180b1cd80d.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/26d249099e240aac89bdddbef7937b266937e448/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--f4b1193f-0cfe-429b-be60-e3180b1cd80d.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0723.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0723.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0722","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0722.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0922","title":"Allaire ColdFusion Server 4.0 源代码泄露漏洞","description":"ColdFusion Server 4.0 的示例应用程序中存在源代码泄露漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过直接访问 sourcewindow.cfm 文件获取服务器端脚本源码。该漏洞源于示例应用未对 sourcewindow.cfm 文件进行访问控制，攻击者可利用此漏洞窃取敏感业务逻辑、数据库连接信息等，为进一步攻击提供情报支撑。影响 Adobe ColdFusion Server 4.0 版本，建议删除或限制对示例目录的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0922"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.130","remediation":"删除 ColdFusion Server 安装目录下的 `CFIDE/exampleapps` 示例应用文件夹，或在 Web 服务器（IIS/Apache）层面添加访问控制规则，禁止外部访问 `/CFIDE/` 路径。同时建议升级到 Adobe 官方仍在支持的最新 ColdFusion 版本（2023 及以上），该版本已移除所有示例应用并默认启用安全配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.allaire.com/handlers/index.cfm?ID=8739&Method=Full","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0922.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0922","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0922.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/263f37bc67cd24fe03a39077d8b57f3001369a95/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0922.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jvpm-rcff-7974/GHSA-jvpm-rcff-7974.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0922.json","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/26d249099e240aac89bdddbef7937b266937e448/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0922.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--23edbec0-a096-44bc-8693-7f4a3b6c06e6.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0722.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0722.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0722.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0552","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0552.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0805","title":"Novell NetWare 4.11 事务跟踪系统拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 4.11 及更早版本的事务跟踪系统（Transaction Tracking System，TTS）存在拒绝服务漏洞。TTS 用于在数据库等事务操作中保证数据一致性，但该组件在处理客户端请求时缺乏有效的资源消耗限制。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过网络向目标 NetWare 服务器发送大量特殊构造的 TTS 相关请求，耗尽系统资源或触发异常处理，导致服务器无法响应正常服务请求，进而造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行 Novell NetWare 4.11 及更早版本并启用 TTS 服务的系统，攻击仅需网络可达且无需合法凭据，利用门槛较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0805"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.650","remediation":"建议将 Novell NetWare 升级至 4.11 之后的修复版本（如 NetWare 5.x），或安装 Novell 官方发布的 TTS 服务相关补丁。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙/路由器上限制对 NetWare 服务器 524 端口（NCP）及 TTS 相关服务的访问，仅允许受信任内网主机连接，并配置连接速率限制与并发请求上限，以降低远程大量请求触发拒绝服务的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1999_2/0439.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2184","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0e46881568ba1d1c2011ec61282a082880cda856/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0805.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0552.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0535","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0535.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0800","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16304,\"outputTokens\":34,\"totalTokens\":16338}}","description":"Allaire Forums 2.0.4 版本中的 GetFile.cfm 脚本存在任意文件读取漏洞。该脚本未对用户输入的文件路径参数进行充分的合法性校验与访问控制，导致未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过构造恶意的 HTTP 请求，向 GetFile.cfm 传递特殊参数来读取 Web 服务器上本不应公开的文件内容，如配置文件、源代码或敏感数据。攻击者可利用此漏洞进行信息探测与进一步攻击，影响范围涵盖运行 Allaire Forums 2.0.4 的服务器，攻击条件仅需网络可达目标且能访问该 CGI 页面即可。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0800"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.037","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Allaire Forums 2.0.5 或更高版本，或升级至 Macromedia/Adobe 后续版本的 ColdFusion 论坛模块。若无法升级，请立即删除或重命名 GetFile.cfm 文件，或在 Web 服务器层面配置访问控制拦截对 GetFile.cfm 的所有请求，同时配置 ColdFusion 沙箱安全限制文件系统读取权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/1998-1999/msg00332.html","http://www.allaire.com/handlers/index.cfm?ID=9602&Method=Full","http://www.osvdb.org/944","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1748","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19193","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe807f4098db5a5ad8dcb41a479197724cb9e789/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0800.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0800","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0800.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f7f250b0cc5cc23741447612a2f182f04c36db78/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0800.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v35h-xh8g-q7r7/GHSA-v35h-xh8g-q7r7.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/ftp.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0800.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_150600_150700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0535.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0513","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0513.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0784","title":"Oracle Database Server TNSLSNR SQL*Net Listener 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Oracle Database Server 7.1.4 和 7.3.3 版本的 TNSLSNR SQL*Net 监听器存在拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者可向监听器端口发送特制的畸形字符串，导致监听器进程崩溃或停止响应，从而使数据库服务不可用。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程触发，影响范围限于上述特定 Oracle 版本。CVSS 基础评分 5.0（中等严重），主要影响可用性，不涉及机密性或完整性破坏。建议升级至修复版本或限制监听器端口的网络访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0784"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.073","remediation":"升级 Oracle Database Server 至 7.3.4 或更高版本，或应用 Oracle 官方补丁补丁 NERP 补丁包。若无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面限制 TNS Listener 端口(默认 1521)仅允许受信任 IP 访问，或在 listener.ora 中配置 VALID_NODE_CHECKING_REGISTRATION=ON 并配置 INVITED_NODES 限制注册节点，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1998_4/0764.html","http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1999_1/0056.html","http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/1998/msg00536.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/19dfa989c2a07b8fd71870a139a7d171f621ff41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0784.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0784","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0784.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9ef5a1e2753195eb4be450895da310f7a8a6524e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0784.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5g3f-rxgg-3554/GHSA-5g3f-rxgg-3554.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0784.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0784.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/95667eace3f4d053cefbe6b54fe10b3647ab0f79/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0513.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0471","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0471.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0757","title":"Allaire ColdFusion Server 弱加密导致 CFML 模板可被解密漏洞","description":"Allaire ColdFusion Server 4.0.1 及更早版本自带的 CFCRYPT.EXE 工具使用强度极弱的加密算法对 CFML 模板源码进行加密保护，攻击者可在本地或获取加密文件后，利用已公开的逆向算法将其解密，从而泄露应用程序的源代码、数据库凭据与业务逻辑。该漏洞的攻击前提是攻击者需能够访问经加密的 CFM 模板文件或安装目录，属于本地信息泄露类问题，不会直接导致远程代码执行，因此危害等级较低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0757"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","remediation":"升级至受官方支持的 ColdFusion 版本（如 ColdFusion 2023 或 2021），彻底弃用已停止维护的 ColdFusion 4.0.1；将 CFML 源码从弱加密保护改为由操作系统文件访问控制列表（ACL）限制读取，并避免在源码中硬编码数据库凭据，改用加密配置文件或环境变量存储敏感信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.allaire.com/handlers/index.cfm?ID=10969&Method=Full","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2208","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19220"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0471.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0317","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0317.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0718","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9087,\"outputTokens\":16,\"totalTokens\":10831}}","description":"IBM GINA for NT 1.0 在作为 Windows NT 用户进行 OS/2 域认证时存在权限提升漏洞。该组件会在本地注册表中维护用于域用户到本地组映射的 GroupMapping 注册表项，且未对此注册表项施加充分的访问控制。已在本机拥有普通用户权限的本地攻击者，可通过修改（或篡改）该 GroupMapping 注册表键值，将自身账号映射至管理员组，从而绕过正常的权限分配机制，非法获取本地管理员（administrator）权限。受影响范围为使用 IBM GINA 1.0 并启用 OS/2 域认证方式的 Windows NT 系统，攻击者需具备目标主机的本地登录权限及对相关注册表项的写权限方可实施利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0718"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.707","remediation":"立即升级 IBM GINA for NT 至修复版本（1.0 之后的补丁版本），或停用该 GINA 组件改用标准 Windows NT 登录认证；通过注册表编辑器对 HKLM\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\Winlogon 下的 GroupMapping 项设置仅 Administrators 拥有完全控制权限、普通用户仅只读，并启用 NTFS 权限审计以阻止本地用户篡改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9908&L=ntbugtraq&F=&S=&P=5534","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/608","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3166","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19472","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64d76d92cfbd9c4de4a352a59a2e52cadebc3afd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0718.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/89b3a1c34ab26afed5cfe4fc54b61cecbf09d3c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0718.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0718","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0718.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0718.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/ec2efce98d544aa857266906f720ae32e42b21be/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-07xx/CVE-1999-0718.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/3b50720431dce1650cc5e5fe96631e7b01e9d02e/1999/CVE-1999-0718.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0718.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0718.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0718.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0317.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0317.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0317.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0234","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0234.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0681","title":"Microsoft FrontPage Personal Web Server 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft FrontPage Server Extensions（PWS）3.0.2.926 在 Windows 95 及可能其他版本上存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，即可通过向目标 Web 服务器发送特制的超长 URL 请求触发该溢出，导致 PWS 服务进程异常终止，引发拒绝服务（Denial of Service），使 Web 服务完全不可用。该漏洞影响安装了受影响版本 FrontPage Server Extensions 的 Windows 系统，攻击条件简单，仅需向 PWS 的 HTTP 接口发送构造的恶意请求即可完成利用，无需任何登录凭据或特殊权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0681"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.150","remediation":"升级 Microsoft FrontPage Server Extensions 至 3.0.2.926 之后的修补版本，或安装 Microsoft 针对该缓冲区溢出的官方安全补丁（参考 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-0xx 及知识库文章 KB238453）。若无法立即更新，可在 Internet Information Services 或 Personal Web Server 的 URL 验证配置中限制请求 URL 的最大长度，或在防火墙层面禁止外部直接访问 FrontPage Server Extensions 端口（默认 80/443），仅允许内网可信 IP 访问，以此作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1999-q3/0381.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/568","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3117","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19445","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6bde90e50f9c8511feb5459f87a55fa56411bd2c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0681.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0681","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0681.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5d448b12fda744aa8491fddc8705260f2b4289f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0681.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5bd4fceb27857756215e988f4824b12d3de84ec1/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wj24-pvf2-wxpm/GHSA-wj24-pvf2-wxpm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_150600_150700.json","https://github.com/CERTCC/SBOM/blob/ae581e32992458f65018df4eced684b7370bba39/SwiftBOM/cpe_lookup/cve_lookup/microsoft/personal_web_server_cve.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0681.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0234.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0234.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0234.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0025","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0025.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0359","title":"Marc Schaefer ptylogin 拒绝服务及密码泄露漏洞","description":"Unix 系统中的 ptylogin 工具存在访问控制缺陷，本地用户可通过操纵伪终端设备锁定调制解调器，导致合法用户无法拨入（拒绝服务）；亦可利用该缺陷以调制解调器身份向外拨号，或截获拨入用户的登录密码。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，影响所有使用 ptylogin 管理串行拨号会话的 Unix 系统，攻击者需具备本地 shell 访问权限即可实施攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0359"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.617","remediation":"立即升级 ptylogin 至最新安全版本；同时移除 ptylogin 二进制文件的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/ptylogin），并将可执行权限限制为仅授权用户组。对调制解调器设备文件（/dev/ttyS*、/dev/modem）设置 600 权限，仅允许 root 和拨号用户组访问。实施回拨认证机制作为临时缓解措施，并建议用 SSH 或 VPN 替代基于调制解调器的远程接入方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0359","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0359.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0359","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0359.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0359.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vwjf-9p53-995f/GHSA-vwjf-9p53-995f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0359.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c